methods.name: app_getNativeDepositAddress
methods.summary: Creates a deposit address related to the host blockchain address passed as a parameter.
methods.description: Creates a native deposit address related to the host blockchain address passed as a parameter. This method works only for UTXO bridges where pNetwork requires a deposit address for swapping between native and host blockchains.

schema.title: host address
schema.description: A host UTXO bridge address that will be associated with the generated native deposit address

result.description: An object containing information about the newly created native deposit address

nativeDepositAddress.description: The generated native deposit address associated with the input host address
